</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Linksys Atlas Pro 6 雙頻網狀 Wi-Fi 6 系統，手機 App 零知識新手設置示範</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/23/linksys-atlas-pro-6-review/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=linksys-atlas-pro-6-review</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[AIpower]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 09:25:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[家居無線]]></category><category><![CDATA[Linksys]]></category><category><![CDATA[網狀 Wi-Fi]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070259</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>好多朋友都想屋企的 Wi-Fi 無線網絡，能夠覆蓋到家中每一處地方，無論客廳、睡房、廁所至到廚房都收得一樣快速 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p2">好多朋友都想屋企的 Wi-Fi 無線網絡，能夠覆蓋到家中每一處地方，無論客廳、睡房、廁所至到廚房都收得一樣快速。企業網絡、無線連接產品大廠 Linksys 近日推出了最新 Wi-Fi 6 產品「Linksys Atlas Pro 6」雙頻網狀 Wi-Fi 6 系統，每個節點的可覆蓋率高達 2,700 平方呎，可同時連接 30 多部裝置，提供快捷串流、遊戲以及無間斷視像通話體驗。以下小編就會實際同大家試玩一下這套新系統。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p1">一買即裝即用，家居無線網絡即可延伸</h2><p class="p1">Linksys Atlas Pro 6 雙頻網狀 Wi-Fi 6 系統，它們都採用最新 Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) 標準，6 個並行空間串流，令傳輸速度達到 5.4Gbps。除了客廳，連露台以至室外用戶都能感受到千兆 Wi-Fi 傳輸速度。此機更可通過添加額外節點擴展家居網絡的 Wi-Fi 覆蓋範圍，形成 Mesh 網絡。今次小編拆開這套網路系統的包裝，就發現已跟來了兩個節點。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070285" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>對應 160MHz 頻寬、採用最新 Qualcomm 處理器</h2><p class="p1">Atlas Pro 6 的 5GHz 頻譜對應 160MHz 頻寬，為你用上擁擠最少的通道，並採用 Velop Intelligent Mesh 技術，每個節點可覆蓋 2,700 平方呎，同時為 30 多部裝置提串流、遊戲、視像通話。要真正發揮 Wi-Fi 6 性能，令到家中多名成員同時上網、工作、網上學習、影音串流、打機都不會遇上頻寬不足的問題。</p><p>而另一方面 Atlas Pro 6 採用了目前 Qualcomm 最新處理器「Qualcomm 沉浸式家庭 216 平台」， 提供更快的連線速度以及穩定性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-694x552.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="552" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-694x552.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-1132x900.jpg 1132w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-768x611.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-1536x1221.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1-2048x1629.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/badge_qcom_immersive_home_216-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>兼容 Linksys MR、WHW、MX 系列靈活性高</h2><p>今次介紹的 Linksys Atlas Pro 6 能夠與 Linksys 旗下的 MX、MR 及 WHW 系列路由器互連組合，把你現有的網路升級為 Mesh Wi-Fi。現有用戶不需要更換路由器，即可馬上為家居無線網路升級。</p><h2 class="p1">網路設置好輕鬆<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>甚至無需網路知識</h2><p class="p1">用戶可藉由免費的 Linksys 應用程式輕鬆設置 Wi-Fi 系統，並從任何地方接入網絡，優先保留更多頻寬給對 Wi-Fi 需求較高的裝置。只要把節點插上電，在手機 App 上我們很快就可完成設置網狀 Wi-Fi 系統，你甚至無需任何複雜的網路知識。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070261 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0043-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲透過手機 App 你可管理與輕鬆設置家居網路</p><h2 class="p1">Step 1</h2><p class="p1">要設置 Linksys Atlas Pro 6 雙頻網狀 Wi-Fi 6 系統其實非常簡單，從 App Store 或 Google Play 商店下載「Linksys」手機 App，打開 App 就會引導你設置網狀 Wi-Fi 系統。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070268 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0000-1-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2 class="p1">Step 2</h2><p class="p1">今時今日安裝家居網絡，幾乎無需學懂如「IP 位址」這類複雜的網絡名詞。Linksys 就用到了藍牙功能，連接非常接近手機的網絡裝置。你首要開啟藍牙使用授權給手機 App，手機就能找到你需要設定的主機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070269 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-3-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070267 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0040-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0040-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0040-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0040.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 class="p1">Step 3</h2><p class="p1">App 內會逐步引導你安裝，物理上你需要為主機插電線，再連接網路線（到現有路由器或上網 modem 機），連擺放位置 App 都會提醒。每過一步，都會詢問你是否看到路由器上的燈號。例如首插電源，路由器會發出紫光。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1070264 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-16.05.25.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="579" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070265 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0041-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0041-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0041-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0041-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 class="p1">Step 4</h2><p class="p1">然後在手機 App 內登記一個 Linksys 帳戶（留待日後管理 Wi-Fi 系統使用）；</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070270 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2 class="p1">Step 5</h2><p class="p1">再為 Wi-Fi 系統設定保安密碼；</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-1-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2 class="p1">Step 6</h2><p class="p1">為這個網路節點起一個名字，或說明它放在你家居哪一個位置（如客廳），你的第一個節點就大功告成。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070272" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-1-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2 class="p1">安裝第二個節點兩步完成</h2><p class="p1">Linksys Atlas Pro 6 雙頻網狀 Wi-Fi 6 系統包裝已跟來了 2 個節點，因此你可在家居另一個地方設置另一個主機。在接上電源後，把手機放近主機，就可做第二個節點的設定。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0035.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0035-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0035-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0035-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0035.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0034.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0034-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0034-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0034-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0034.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p1">所有設置完成後，你的家居網路就能通過這個新節點而得到延伸。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0032-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070274" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0032-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0032-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0032-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0032-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p1">延伸 Wi-Fi 覆蓋範圍<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>在門外上網有如在室內</h2><p class="p1">筆者辦公室的路由器放置於辦公室中心，要到門口，甚至門外的洗手間上網，單靠辦公室中心的路由器就有點困難。現在筆者就把第二個節點放在門口位置。</p><p class="p1">經過網速測試，發現在門口位置，以至門口外再進洗手間，網速都好像身處辦公室內一樣，網速達到 330Mbps，比起辦公室內實測的 385Mbps 網速非常接近。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0028-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0028-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0028-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0039-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p class="p1">Wi-Fi 系統也提供進階的保安以及家長監護功能，成為家庭升級網絡系統時的理想選擇。在管理 App 中你可加入受管理的裝置，可設定此裝置的上網時間，以及封鎖指定網域。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-16.14.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1070281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-16.14.51.jpg" alt="" width="538" height="580" /></a></p><p class="p1">今次的測試令筆者感受到其實設定無線網路，比以前簡單了好多，用智能手機貼近主機，就能輕鬆設定（設定完成後它就受到加密保護，所以不會容易被入侵），也證明了裝設了這些網狀 Wi-Fi 系統後，家居無線網路的發射範圍馬上可得到延伸。如果你也有這樣的需要，不妨考慮為自己的家居安裝這類網狀 Wi-Fi 系統。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
